title: Rangers in playoffs, near AL West title after edging Angels (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 53,993 Rangers in playoffs, near AL West title after edging Angels (Yahoo Sports) ARLINGTON, Texas (AP) -- The Texas Rangers clinched a wild-card spot and moved to the cusp of the AL West title, with Adrian Beltre's three-run double backing Derek Holland in a 5-3 victory over the Los Angeles Angels on Thursday night.
